    @ PSC=7999: 8MHz / (7999+1) = 1kHz -> each tick = 1ms
    @ LED1 (PE8): toggles every LED1_HALF_PERIOD ms  (default 500ms -> 1Hz blink)
    @ LED2 (PE9): toggles every LED2_HALF_PERIOD ms  (default 100ms -> 5Hz blink)
